# WB::NewWhiteboard --
#
#       Makes a unique whiteboard.
#
# Arguments:
#       args    -file fileName
#               -state normal|disabled 
#               -title name
#               -usewingeom 0|1
#               ?-key value ...? custom arguments
#       
# Results:
